data.text:
Tyler Hansbrough - Points

Tyler Hansbrough scores a career high 49 points (2019)

On December 13, 2019, Tyler Hansbrough set his career high in points in a China - CBA game. That day he scored 49 points in Sichuan's home win against Jiangsu, 108-105. He also had 22 rebounds, 5 steals. He shot 15/29 from two, 0/2 from three, shooting at 48.4% from the field. He also shot 19/23 from the free-throw line.

Tyler Hansbrough - Rebounds

Tyler Hansbrough grabs a career high 26 rebounds (2018)

On December 11, 2018, Tyler Hansbrough set his career high in rebounds in a China - CBA game. That day he grabbed 26 rebounds in Zhejiang's road loss against Shanghai, 90-67. He also had 30 points, 3 assists, 2 steals and 1 block.

Tyler Hansbrough - Assists

Tyler Hansbrough gives a career high 6 assists (2006)

On November 24, 2006, Tyler Hansbrough set his career high in assists in a NCAA game. That day he dished 6 assists in North Carolina Tar Heels's home win against Tennessee Volunteers, 101-87. He also had 27 points, 9 rebounds, 1 steal.

Tyler Hansbrough - Steals

Tyler Hansbrough has a career high 5 steals (2019)

On December 13, 2019, Tyler Hansbrough tied his career high in steals in a China - CBA game. That day he reached 5 steals in Sichuan's home win against Jiangsu, 108-105. He also had 49 points, 22 rebounds.

Tyler Hansbrough - Blocks

Tyler Hansbrough blocks a career high 4 shots (2018)

On February 09, 2018, Tyler Hansbrough set his career high in blocks in a China - CBA game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Guangzhou's home win against Liaoning, 120-114. He also had 18 points, 18 rebounds.
